To make repo cloned as http use ssh when pushing (ie no password)


    git remote -v
    git remote set-url origin git@github.com:tomgdow/RichInternetApplication

    See here http://stackoverflow.com/a/18798272/499167

TO CHANGE BACK AGAIN
    git remote set-url origin https://github.com/tomGdow/dotvimrc.git

    see https://stackoverflow.com/q/50020142/499167

